Author: situationtypedill
Text: I was eating healthy and working out and losing weight and then this week I had a hypomanic episode and now I’m super depressed and haven’t been tracking what I eat and I haven’t worked out in a week and now I don’t know what to do and I’m scared to weigh myself. I haven’t been binge eating but I’ve been eating unhealthy foods and eating more than I had been so I’m sure I’ve gained weight
